---
/**
 * AgentFlowContainer.astro
 * UI-only demo flow for WikiSure™
 * Perspective: Platform Provider
 * Product: Embedded Insurance
 * Context: Germany (fixed, non-selectable)
 */
---

<section class="flow">

  <h1>WikiSure™ Demo Flow</h1>
  <p class="intro">
    This demo shows a <strong>single governed semantic decision</strong>
    from the perspective of a <strong>platform provider</strong>
    operating an <strong>embedded insurance product</strong> in Germany.
  </p>

  <!-- STEP 1 -->
  <div class="step">
    <h2>1. Define</h2>
    <p>
      A key term is introduced that affects contracts, data exchange
      and regulatory interpretation.
    </p>
    <div class="box">
      <strong>Term:</strong> “Coverage Activation”
      <br />
      <em>Initial canonical definition is documented.</em>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 2 -->
  <div class="step">
    <h2>2. Propose Change</h2>
    <p>
      A partner proposes a refined interpretation based on operational needs.
    </p>
    <div class="box">
      <em>Proposed change:</em>
      Coverage starts at vehicle handover instead of contract signature.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 3 -->
  <div class="step">
    <h2>3. Review</h2>
    <p>
      Stakeholders review the proposal from different perspectives:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Platform operations</li>
      <li>Insurance partner</li>
      <li>Compliance & regulation</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="note">
      AI may assist by highlighting conflicts — humans remain accountable.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 4 -->
  <div class="step">
    <h2>4. Governance Decision</h2>
    <p>
      A governed decision is made with explicit conditions.
    </p>
    <div class="box decision">
      ✔ Accepted with conditions<br />
      • Documentation updated<br />
      • Partner alignment required<br />
      • Regulatory note attached
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 5 -->
  <div class="step">
    <h2>5. Outcome</h2>
    <p>
      The validated definition becomes reusable across systems,
      contracts and AI processes.
    </p>
    <p class="highlight">
      Shared meaning → Faster decisions → Clear accountability
    </p>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
.flow {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 40px 24px;
}

.intro {
  color: #4b5563;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.step {
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.box {
  background: #f9fafb;
  border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 16px;
  margin-top: 12px;
}

.decision {
  background: #ecfeff;
  border-color: #67e8f9;
}

.note {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #6b7280;
}

.highlight {
  font-weight: 600;
}
</style>
